multimedia/htpc-manager includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/htpc-manager

TO START HTPC-MANAGER ON BOOT:
echo 'htpc_manager_enable="YES"' >> /etc/rc.conf

START MANUALLY:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/htpc-manager start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:8085/

